Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:20.36,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(321,378)}{\bord2}{\fad(531,353)\pos(227,380)\3c&H008000&}這次也在白子的地盤裏黑子有棋可走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:21.51,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真唯來試一試
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:26.41,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被叫吃了 所以我連起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:28.52,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:30.06,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我下這裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:31.11,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:32.79,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\3c&HD554E9&\bord2\fad(331,200)\pos(305,379)}真唯 真可惜!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.69,0:22:32.64,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼也吃不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:35.33,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優希來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.44,0:22:36.02,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:39.96,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被叫吃 所以連起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:43.22,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是被叫吃 我再連起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:47.06,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這樣白子逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:48.30,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:51.14,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得不錯 這是正確的下法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:51.14,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\fad(131,111)\3c&HCB0000&\bord2\pos(310,385)}優希吃了很多子啊!!
